Release:	1
License:	GPL v2+
Group:		Applications/Publishing
Source0:	http://dl.sourceforge.net/gnochm/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	ad2bcf1acf5bd2b7f7eee806a0c9859f
